import Head from 'next/head'
import Layout from '../components/Layout'
const Index =()=>{
    return (
        <Layout>
            <React.Fragment>
            <Head>
            <title>Home </title>
            <meta name="viewport" content="initial-scale=1.0, width=device-width" />
            </Head>
            
        </React.Fragment>
        </Layout>
    )
}

export default Index
